<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>فَصْلٌ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>- الصَّيْدُ مُبَاحٌ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>-<span class="c5"> وَشُرُوطُهُ أَرْبَعَةٌ:</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c4">[١]</span> كَوْنُ صَائِدٍ مِنْ أَهْلِ ذَكَاةٍ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c4">[٢]</span> وَالآلَةُ،<span class="c5"> وَهِيَ:</span><a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>١) آلَةُ ذَكَاةٍ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>٢) أَوْ جَارِحٌ مُعَلَّمٌ.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>-<span class="c5"> وَهُوَ:</span> أَنْ يَسْتَرْسِلَ إِذَا أُرْسِلَ، ويَنْزَجِرَ إِذَا زُجِرَ، وَإِذَا أَمْسَكَ لَمْ يَأْكُلْ.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c4">[٣]</span> وَإِرْسَالُهَا قَاصِداً، فَلَوِ اسْتَرْسَلَ جَارِحٌ بِنَفْسِهِ،<span class="c5"> فَقَتَلَ صَيْداً:</span> لَمْ يَحِلَّ.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c4">[٤]</span> وَالتَّسْمِيَةُ عِنْدَ رَمْيٍ أَوْ إِرْسَالٍ.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>- وَلَا تَسْقُطُ بِحَالٍ.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>- وَسُنَّ تَكْبِيرٌ مَعَهَا.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>- وَمَنْ أَعْتَقَ صَيْداً،<span class="c5"> أَوْ أَرْسَلَ بَعِيراً أَوْ غَيْرَهُ:</span> لَمْ يَزُلْ مِلْكُهُ عَنْهُ.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>